quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  42,1,"Hā mīm.",""
  42,2,"‘Aēn sīn ƙọ̄f. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1."
  42,3,"Báyẹn ni Allāhu, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n ṣe ń fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí ìwọ àti àwọn tó ṣíwájú rẹ.<sup>1</sup>","[1] È é ti ṣe tí Allāhu lẹ́yìn tí Ó sọ pé “Báyẹn ni Allāhu, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n ṣe ń fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí ìwọ àti àwọn tó ṣíwájú rẹ.” kò fi kún un pé, “àti àwọn tó ń bọ̀ lẹ́yìn rẹ”? Ìdí ni pé, Allāhu ti fi Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - ṣe òpin àwọn arímìísígbà “kātamu-nnabiyyīn”. Ẹ wo sūrah al-’Ahzāb; 33:40."
  42,4,"TiRẹ̀ ni ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀. Ó ga, Ó tóbi.",""
  42,5,"Sánmọ̀ fẹ́ẹ̀ fàya láti òkè wọn (nípa títóbi Allāhu). Àwọn mọlāika sì ń ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú ẹyìn fún Olúwa wọn. Wọ́n sì ńtọrọ àforíjìn fún àwọn tó wà lórí ilẹ̀. Gbọ́, dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.",""
  42,6,"Àwọn tó mú àwọn alátìlẹ́yìn kan lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀, Allāhu sì ni Aláàbò lórí wọn. Ìwọ sì kọ́ ni olùṣọ́ lórí wọn.",""
  42,7,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe fi al-Ƙur’ān ránṣẹ́ sí ọ ní èdè Lárúbáwá nítorí kí o lè fi ṣe ìkìlọ̀ fún ’Ummul-Ƙurọ̄ (ìyẹn, ará ìlú Mọkkah) àti ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá wà ní àyíká rẹ̀ (ìyẹn, ará ìlú yòókù), àti nítorí kí o lè fi ṣe ìkìlọ̀ nípa Ọjọ́ Àkójọ, tí kò sí iyèméjì nínú rẹ̀. Ìjọ kan yóò wà nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra. Ìjọ kan yó sì wà nínú Iná tó ń jò.",""
  42,8,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu bá fẹ́, ìbá ṣe wọ́n ní ìjọ ẹlẹ́sìn ẹyọ kan. Ṣùgbọ́n Ó ń fi ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́ sínú ìkẹ́ Rẹ̀. Àwọn alábòsí, kò sì níí sí aláàbò àti alárànṣe kan fún wọn.",""
  42,9,"Ṣé wọ́n mú àwọn aláàbò kan lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀ ni? Allāhu, Òun sì ni Aláàbò. Òun l’Ó ń sọ àwọn òkú di alààyè. Òun sì ni Alágbára lórí gbogbo n̄ǹkan.",""
  42,10,"Ohunkóhun tí ẹ bá yapa-ẹnu lórí rẹ̀, ìdájọ́ rẹ̀ di ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu. Ìyẹn ni Allāhu, Olúwa mi. Òun ni mo gbáralé. Ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ sì ni mo máa ṣẹ́rí padà sí (ní ti ìronúpìwàdà). <sup>1</sup>","[1] Ìyẹn ni pe, kí á ṣẹ́rí gbogbo àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ tí ìyapa-ẹnu bá wáyé lórí wọn sínú al-Ƙur’ān, ọ̀rọ̀ Allāhu àti ìdájọ́ Rẹ̀."
